Extension:BOFH                                        by Helmut K. C. Tessarek
--------------

This extension adds a tag and a function to display a random BOFH excuse

Installation
------------

cd extensions
git clone https://github.com/tessus/mwExtensionBOFH.git BOFH

Then add to the bottom of your LocalSettings.php file:

# Extension:BOFH
wfLoadExtension('BOFH');

Usage
-----

Add a <bofh/> tag wherever you want a randomly-generated BOFH excuse to appear.

A function can be used to display a random excuse in a nostalgic look:

{{bofh:}}

Without a value the width of the box will be the length of the excuse, but you can
also specify a fixed length {{bofh:600}} or percentage {{bofh:40%}}.
